run imageBasics.cpp under bulid/:
cmake ..
make
./imageBasics

The RGB images, X channel, Y channel and Z channel are stored in bulid/matlab 828/.
From 0 to 2: X channel, Y channel and Z channel

bulid/
000.png and 001.png are original pictures.
00, 01,02,03,04.png are road pictures used for testing.
1,2,3,4,5.png are wrong pictures.

bulid/ori_pic_data/
more original pictures 

bulid/matlab/data/
input files of 5 coordinates

bulid/datapic_roadtest/
data and pictures used for road testing.
